Description: MurOS firewall and routing platform
 MurOS is an OPNsense fork ported to Debian. It provides a web-managed
 stateful firewall (nftables), NAT, interfaces and routing on top of a
 standard Debian base, using systemd, apt and iproute2.
 .
 The whole system configuration is owned by this package, so appliance
 defaults (php-fpm pool sizing, kernel forwarding) do not drift back to
 distribution defaults.
